---
import Card from '../ui/Card.astro';
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="section-padding animate-on-scroll">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="section-title text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 gradient-text">
      Sobre Mí
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="about-content stagger-container">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Soy un desarrollador apasionado por crear experiencias digitales innovadoras, 
          combinando desarrollo web moderno con tecnologías inmersivas como VR, AR y 3D.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Mi enfoque se centra en construir soluciones que no solo funcionen perfectamente, 
          sino que también inspiren y sorprendan a los usuarios.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/cv.pdf" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover-lift transition-all duration-300">
          <span>Descargar CV</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-image relative">
        <div class="image-container card-3d">
          <div class="card-3d-inner">
            <img 
              src="/placeholder.svg?height=400&width=400" 
              alt="Foto de perfil" 
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-sm mx-auto"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-500/20 to-purple-600/20 rounded-2xl"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-padding {
    padding: 100px 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -10px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 100px;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00d4ff, #ff6b6b);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .image-container {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: -20px;
    right: 20px;
    bottom: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00d4ff, #ff6b6b);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.3;
    animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 0.5; }
  }
</style>
